    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="1">
        <title>Mud Guards</title>
        <para>The mud guards (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0901011">Figure 11, Item 1</hotlnk>) on the 3300 Series bus chassis are located at the
            bottom of the fender extension assembly on each side of the chassis. The mud guards help minimize the damage
            to the lower edge of the cowl and body components.
        </para>
